one_reviews_text:
5 minutes and then... no interest.
Bad graphics, even the raptor is awful.
It's a okay game, keeps you busy for a little while.

review_title: Keeps you busy... for a few minutes
one_reviews_text: I'll give it 4 stars, it's nothing mind blowing but the concept is cool, the survival mechanics actually reminded me of 5 nights at freddy's. It'll keep you busy for a few minutes. I will say it's awful short though and the raphics are far from perfect. I hope there will be more content!
Very scary! However the developer shouldn't use pure blacks beause they smear on OLED displays.
